comments: Mrs Gartrell is great! The papers are all easy and whoever said otherwise is a big pussy. I got an easy A in this class and she\'s fun to get to know. Great teacher.

You have to write seven papers and take tests during the quarter, and you only have a few minutes to finish the tests. She doesn\'t allow rewrites after the first two papers. She converts sentences into math formulas and computer code to confuse students even more. The only way you may get an A is if this is your only class.
